org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore

Class ColumnType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.ColumnType

  • @InterfaceAudience.Public
 @InterfaceStability.Stable
public class ColumnType
extends Object
    Constants and utility functions for column types. This is explicitly done as constants in the class rather than an enum in order to interoperate with Hive's old serdeConstants. All type names in this class match the type names in Hive's serdeConstants class. They must continue to do so.
